# Hybrid Retrieval Engine — Walkthrough

## What Was Built

The **Layer 7 — Hybrid Retrieval Engine** for HelioX RAG 3.0, implementing a 4-stage retrieval cascade per architecture blueprint §2.7.

## Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD
    SQO["Locked SQO"] --> S1["Stage 1: Metadata Filter<br/>(PostgreSQL)"]
    S1 --> S2["Stage 2: Entity Overlap<br/>(In-Memory)"]
    S2 --> S3["Stage 3: Vector Search<br/>(Qdrant)"]
    S3 --> SCORE["Score & Rank"]
    SCORE --> CHECK{"recall < 0.60?"}
    CHECK -->|Yes| S4["Stage 4: Fallback<br/>(Broad Search)"]
    S4 --> SCORE
    CHECK -->|No| DK["Dynamic K<br/>(Coverage Gain)"]
    DK --> CONF["Confidence<br/>Estimation"]
    CONF --> RESULT["RetrievalResult"]
```

## Files Created

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| [config.py](file:///c:/HelioX/retrieval/config.py) | All tuning knobs (scoring weights, blend weights, dynamic K params) |
| [schemas.py](file:///c:/HelioX/retrieval/schemas.py) | DTOs: [ScoredChunk](file:///c:/HelioX/retrieval/schemas.py#36-63), [ScoreBreakdown](file:///c:/HelioX/retrieval/schemas.py#20-29), [RetrievalResult](file:///c:/HelioX/retrieval/schemas.py#117-130), [RetrievalConfidence](file:///c:/HelioX/retrieval/schemas.py#84-92) |
| [scoring.py](file:///c:/HelioX/retrieval/scoring.py) | Recency decay, query coverage, weighted score formula |
| [metadata_filter.py](file:///c:/HelioX/retrieval/metadata_filter.py) | Stage 1: PostgreSQL temporal/geographic/authority filtering |
| [entity_filter.py](file:///c:/HelioX/retrieval/entity_filter.py) | Stage 2: Case-insensitive entity overlap ≥ threshold |
| [vector_search.py](file:///c:/HelioX/retrieval/vector_search.py) | Stage 3: Multi-vector blend (α·semantic + β·entity + γ·HyDE) |
| [fallback.py](file:///c:/HelioX/retrieval/fallback.py) | Stage 4: Broad retrieval when recall < 0.60 |
| [dynamic_k.py](file:///c:/HelioX/retrieval/dynamic_k.py) | Coverage-gain stopping: initial 25 → final K ∈ [5, 12] |
| [engine.py](file:///c:/HelioX/retrieval/engine.py) | Main orchestrator coordinating all stages |
| [__init__.py](file:///c:/HelioX/retrieval/__init__.py) | Package exports |

## Scoring Formula

```
weighted_score =
    0.10 × recency          (exponential decay, half-life 180d)
  + 0.15 × source_rank      (authority_score from profiling)
  + 0.10 × citation_density  (0 on first pass)
  + 0.10 × worker_confidence (0 on first pass)
  + 0.35 × cosine_similarity (blended multi-vector)
  + 0.20 × query_coverage   (entity overlap + keyword match)
```

## Confidence Estimation

```
retrieval_confidence =
    0.30 × recall_estimate
  + 0.30 × avg_cosine_similarity
  + 0.25 × query_coverage
  + 0.15 × candidate_diversity
```

